WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.560
All crew members can view checklists for all roles.

2
00:00:03.560 --> 00:00:06.560
Under the My Jobs icon, click on Details

3
00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:08.480
and then Other Crew Members.

4
00:00:08.480 --> 00:00:12.080
By clicking on each crew member, you can see their checklist.

5
00:00:12.080 --> 00:00:15.760
Only crew leads can mark any checklist item as complete,

6
00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:20.680
but each role is responsible for completing and checking off their tasks.

7
00:00:20.680 --> 00:00:23.080
If a member isn't doing their role,

8
00:00:23.080 --> 00:00:25.640
show them their scope and checklist.

9
00:00:25.640 --> 00:00:29.240
Help others grow as you'd want them to help you.

10
00:00:29.240 --> 00:00:33.080
Your role's checklist will always be the one shown here.

11
00:00:33.080 --> 00:00:37.120
Completing all checklist items ensures a quality job.

12
00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:40.519
As a Tradewize member, take pride in quality work

13
00:00:40.519 --> 00:00:44.160
and help others follow their scope to complete their checklist.

14
00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:49.320
All checklists must be completed and quality verified before anyone gets paid.